Name: Stars Force
About the game: STARS FORCE is a unit created to fight space pirates. In whatever star system the crime occurs, 'STARS FORCE' is in a hurry to put things in order! The player will play as the pilot of a warship fighting hordes of space pirates. Several types of ships and weapons. Collecting items and breaking capsules, you can pump your ship. Features: Pumping the ship 10 types of enemy ships 15 levels 3 locations bosses
